wf_workflow_version.description:
Feedback workflow for TCS (Tieto Cloud Services) Integration. Workflow should update statuses about particular installation tasks. *Inputs: u_operation_id u_configuration_item_sys_id u_integration_location u_integration_command_name u_integration_command_argument_success u_integration_command_argument_failure u_work_notes u_work_notes_must_not_contain u_work_notes_must_contain
*Outputs: exit_code error_message
wf_workflow_version.name: TCS Integration Feedback
wf_workflow_version.on_cancel: // This script executes if the workflow is cancelled.// The global variable context_sys_id contains the sys_id of the cancelled workflow context.
